      "text": "DISTRICT (BSCDD) ZONE (RC-Jun 20/06;E-Jul 29/06) 1) No development permit shall be issued for a development with a Bedford South Comprehensive Development District (BSCDD) Zone except in accordance with a development agreement approved pursuant to policies contained in the Bedford South Secondary Planning Strategy."
